</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" namest="col2" nameend="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Browse to the workstation location where the downloaded Colorado1650_PrintJobViewer_Rx.y.zip file was unzipped 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" namest="col2" nameend="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Double-click Colorado.DotPrintJobViewer.exe to start the application. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The following window displays: 
</p><fig id="GUID-AE5F0D0A-4D76-446C-9624-10D92BDA0297" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-909C7BA6-49AB-4079-A649-A06427A3DB0E-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-909C7BA6-49AB-4079-A649-A06427A3DB0E-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" namest="col2" nameend="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Click Open File in the menu bar to locate and select the .print file to view. 
</p><note id="GUID-6A5C00E2-C8B2-405E-BC80-955FBEC9F4AF" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not attempt to open a Colorado 1640/1650 file. You will get an error about the supported print job version. 
</p></note></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" namest="col2" nameend="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The following window displays: 
</p><fig id="GUID-B8AB287E-049D-4B42-BAC3-F17810C29BE3" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E66F177A-59ED-4B1B-9942-D35B2DED9375-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E66F177A-59ED-4B1B-9942-D35B2DED9375-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-A418658F-08C3-4731-B522-DC595977F9F5" class="- topic/fig "><desc class="- topic/desc "><p class="- topic/p ">Second part of the main screen. 
</p></desc><image href="GUID-7F0C4FDC-8B6F-46D0-ACFE-859CBF685A2C-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-7F0C4FDC-8B6F-46D0-ACFE-859CBF685A2C-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" morerows="16" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" namest="col2" nameend="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Available information and features are: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In the main window: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Job header field names and values (see explanation for each field on the right side) 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> For PrintModeID, see the table below for the Colorado 1635 print mode: 
